                            <comment id="17183568" author="amphied" created="Mon, 24 Aug 2020 19:42:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ggregory&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ggregory&quot;&gt;ggregory&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I propose to restore the handling of collections to its pre-3.11 state.&lt;br/&gt;
I created &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/commons-lang/pull/610&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;pr#610&lt;/a&gt; which pushes the recently-introduced changes for JSON-style down to &lt;tt&gt;JsonToStringStyle&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I added a bunch of test cases to cover non-empty collections, maps, and arrays in various styles.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
